<template>
  <svg
    width="37"
    height="37"
    viewBox="0 0 37 37"
    fill="none"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
  >
    <circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="18.5" fill="url(#pattern0)" />
    <defs>
      <pattern
        id="pattern0"
        patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
        width="1"
        height="1"
      >
        <use xlink:href="#image0" transform="scale(0.00263158)" />
      </pattern>
      <image
        id="image0"
        width="380"
        height="380"
        xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"
      />
    </defs>
  </svg>
</template>
